data.description: Welcome Home to 11 Home Farm Road! Located in a great neighborhood and within walking distance to local shopping and CARY Medical Center. Your new home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms! This home offers lots of room for the whole family to spread out and enjoy! Direct entry from the garage into the laundry/mudroom and right on in to the dining room and kitchen. This country kitchen is big enough for multiple people to cook and move about without bumping into each other. The bright and inviting family room is full of windows and lets in an abundance of natural light. The wood burning fireplace adds a warming touch to enjoy some relaxation and downtime. The living room and family room is a nice big open room yet still kinda their own (when you get here, you will see what I mean). In the living room the patio door offers direct access to the fenced in backyard. A brand new full bath with tub/shower on the main floor as well as a full bath with a shower in the large primary bedroom. The 15x15 primary bedroom also offers double closets and hardwood floors. The other 2 bedrooms on the main floor also have hardwood floors and closets. If the first floor is not enough room for you, wait until you go down to the finished basement. Plenty of space for a workout area, a home office, a second living room or whatever you may need really! You will notice that there is also a wood burning fireplace down here too! The large bedroom is carpeted an offers a full bath and plenty of closets and storage space. Other amenities include radon mitigation system, generator transfer switch and high speed internet is available. You will have plenty of options when it comes to heating your home. Options are fuel oil, electric (heat pump) or wood in the wood burning fireplaces. Contact me today to come and take a look at your new home before its too late!
